					<description><![CDATA[<p>GIM Raises US$20 Million to Expand AI Investment Platform Grace Investment Machine (GIM), an AI-native investment technology company, has raised US$20 million in Series A funding. The round was co-led</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ventureburn.com/gim-raises-us20-million-ai-investment-platform/" data-wpel-link="internal">GIM Raises US$20 Million to Advance AI Investment Systems</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ventureburn.com" data-wpel-link="internal">Ventureburn</a>.</p>
